msgid " Names."
msgstr " Names."

msgid "Nicknames for your characters can be highly desirable. "
msgstr "Nicknames for your characters can be highly desirable. "

msgid ""
"They can help describe someone's personality or appearance with little or no"
" exposition: \"Hey, Red, come here!\" \"Go get Pokey so we can get "
"started.\" "
msgstr ""
"They can help describe someone's personality or appearance with little or no"
" exposition: \"Hey, Red, come here!\" \"Go get Pokey so we can get "
"started.\" "

msgid ""
"They can also set the mood as hostile or friendly or describe the cultural "
"set of an era or a nation. "
msgstr ""
"They can also set the mood as hostile or friendly or describe the cultural "
"set of an era or a nation. "

msgid ""
"They are also excellent \"tags\" that help your reader remember or identify "
"a character. "
msgstr ""
"They are also excellent \"tags\" that help your reader remember or identify "
"a character. "

msgid ""
"Unless it is important to the story, avoid connecting words like tiny, "
"little, bitty, and small to the names of your protagonists. "
msgstr ""
"Unless it is important to the story, avoid connecting words like tiny, "
"little, bitty, and small to the names of your protagonists. "

msgid "The tiny of Tiny Tim is central to the character and his problem. "
msgstr "The tiny of Tiny Tim is central to the character and his problem. "

msgid ""
"Believe me, Little Leroy and Bitsy Betty have problems, too, whether you "
"intended them or not. "
msgstr ""
"Believe me, Little Leroy and Bitsy Betty have problems, too, whether you "
"intended them or not. "

msgid ""
"Psychologically, the diminutive name takes away personal power and "
"emasculates. "
msgstr ""
"Psychologically, the diminutive name takes away personal power and "
"emasculates. "

msgid "Even names like Jimmy or Billy fall into this cabinet."
msgstr "Even names like Jimmy or Billy fall into this cabinet."

msgid " Nonsexist and Nonracist Terminology."
msgstr " Nonsexist and Nonracist Terminology."

msgid ""
"It is good to use generic terminology instead of words that express gender "
"bias. "
msgstr ""
"It is good to use generic terminology instead of words that express gender "
"bias. "

msgid ""
"For example, use mail carrier instead of mailman, and carry that principle "
"to all occupations or positions that end with man. "
msgstr ""
"For example, use mail carrier instead of mailman, and carry that principle "
"to all occupations or positions that end with man. "

msgid "Other things to look out for are usage of the pronoun he. "
msgstr "Other things to look out for are usage of the pronoun he. "

msgid ""
"Even though it is proper to use the masculine pronoun, try to vary it. "
msgstr ""
"Even though it is proper to use the masculine pronoun, try to vary it. "

msgid "You can also use the plural they or the neutral third person you. "
msgstr "You can also use the plural they or the neutral third person you. "

msgid ""
"Both are widely used today to avoid more awkward constructions such as "
"he/she. "
msgstr ""
"Both are widely used today to avoid more awkward constructions such as "
"he/she. "

msgid ""
"Another area to avoid in nonsexist writing is stereotypical roles, such as "
"exclusively male doctors and exclusively female nurses in a hospital "
"setting. "
msgstr ""
"Another area to avoid in nonsexist writing is stereotypical roles, such as "
"exclusively male doctors and exclusively female nurses in a hospital "
"setting. "

msgid ""
"Women and men should be treated the same in all types of stories, as should "
"boys and girls. "
msgstr ""
"Women and men should be treated the same in all types of stories, as should "
"boys and girls. "

msgid "Again, stay away from stereotyping."
msgstr "Again, stay away from stereotyping."

msgid " Diversity."
msgstr " Diversity."

msgid ""
"Race, religion, and physical abilities are other areas where you should be "
"sensitive to word usage. "
msgstr ""
"Race, religion, and physical abilities are other areas where you should be "
"sensitive to word usage. "

msgid ""
"Use African American or of African heritage instead of black, and Native "
"American instead of Indian. "
msgstr ""
"Use African American or of African heritage instead of black, and Native "
"American instead of Indian. "

msgid ""
"Asian American is preferable to Oriental; not all Muslims are Arabs; not all"
" Arabs are Muslim; Hispanics are from the Americas, while Latinos are from "
"any place that speaks Spanish. "
msgstr ""
"Asian American is preferable to Oriental; not all Muslims are Arabs; not all"
" Arabs are Muslim; Hispanics are from the Americas, while Latinos are from "
"any place that speaks Spanish. "

msgid ""
"You get the idea; be sensitive, especially to offensive terminology, and "
"seek out an authority when in doubt. "
msgstr ""
"You get the idea; be sensitive, especially to offensive terminology, and "
"seek out an authority when in doubt. "

msgid ""
"Children enjoy reading about people like themselves, so it's good to have "
"characters with diverse backgrounds. "
msgstr ""
"Children enjoy reading about people like themselves, so it's good to have "
"characters with diverse backgrounds. "

msgid ""
"As noted in the introduction, ethnic, cultural pride, and bilingual books, "
"as well as books with disabled characters, have increased in number though "
"they do not yet constitute a large percentage of the publishing world for "
"juvenile readers. "
msgstr ""
"As noted in the introduction, ethnic, cultural pride, and bilingual books, "
"as well as books with disabled characters, have increased in number though "
"they do not yet constitute a large percentage of the publishing world for "
"juvenile readers. "

msgid ""
"With the tremendous strides the world has taken toward globalization, "
"diversity has become an important part of juvenile literature, and I expect "
"this to grow dramatically in the next few years. "
msgstr ""
"With the tremendous strides the world has taken toward globalization, "
"diversity has become an important part of juvenile literature, and I expect "
"this to grow dramatically in the next few years. "

msgid "Tags. "
msgstr "Tags. "

msgid "An editor may suggest you use a tag to help identify a character. "
msgstr "An editor may suggest you use a tag to help identify a character. "

msgid ""
"Tags are actions or gestures a character typically uses that easily identify"
" the person to the reader. "
msgstr ""
"Tags are actions or gestures a character typically uses that easily identify"
" the person to the reader. "

msgid ""
"A boy may toss his head when he gossips, a young girl may push up her "
"glasses just before she throws a fast pitch. "
msgstr ""
"A boy may toss his head when he gossips, a young girl may push up her "
"glasses just before she throws a fast pitch. "

msgid ""
"The tag may be used to build a character, be part of the problem, or "
"identify a \"mystery\" person. "
msgstr ""
"The tag may be used to build a character, be part of the problem, or "
"identify a \"mystery\" person. "

msgid ""
"For example, a boy may try to hide in the bushes or shadow a suspect while "
"humming the song he always hums or sniffing a chronically runny nose. "
msgstr ""
"For example, a boy may try to hide in the bushes or shadow a suspect while "
"humming the song he always hums or sniffing a chronically runny nose. "

msgid ""
"As noted before, nicknames are another good tag you can use to help describe"
" a character."
msgstr ""
"As noted before, nicknames are another good tag you can use to help describe"
" a character."

